name: Mod Flower Print
description:
Hanging on a wall or standing on a shelf, Messagemark cute and colorful prints will brighten any room at home or work.

Digitally printed onto heavy weight 350gsm recycled (post consumer waste) paper, each print is designed to make you and our earth feel happy!

The affordable range of Wall Art from Messagemark come are designed to fit perfectly into the *RIBBA 30 x 40cm frames from IKEA.

Available in birch, walnut, black, white and silver, there are many options to suit your own interior color schemes. Simply place the print behind the mount board that comes with the *RIBBA frame and voila, instant art!

Each print comes packaged in a cello bag and is posted in a rigid cardboard envelope for protection.

Print Size: 320 x 400mm
Image Size: 210 x 300mm

*RIBBA frame is not included with the print purchase.

name: Retro Mod Postcards
description:
A Postcard is something that hangs around for a while. We find people often keep them next to their desk, stuck on the fridge at home, or even frame as a mini artwork - it is a constant reminder of who sent it to them!

So experiment a little and see if our Postcards can help you to establish a better relationship with a Customer, or use them for a quick note to show your appreciation to someone special.

Pack Includes:
15 x Postcards*
3 Cards in each design from the Retro Mod range
Card Size 105 x 150 mm

Designed and made in Adelaide by Kyrie Kohlhagen using 100% Recycled Paper.

*not supplied with envelopes

name: Retro Christmas Note Cards
description:
The Multi-Card Christmas Pack is the perfect solution for your greeting card supply at home leading up to the festive season. 

Our popular designs appeal to males, females, young and old! When purchased in packs of 10, each card is only $2.50... Not bad for a locally designed and made eco friendly product!

Pack Includes:
10 x Blank Christmas Cards with envelopes
Includes a mix of cards in each design from the Retro Christmas range
Card Size 120 x 175 mm

Designed and made in Adelaide by Kyrie Kohlhagen using 100% Recycled Paper.

name: Polyhedra Garland 'Cut & Fold' Kit
description:
Get crafty at home with our Polyhedra Garland 'Cut & Fold Kit'. Make your own unique geometric paper garland in gorgeous bright colours. Alternatively, you can create a white garland simply by folding the templates inside-out!

Each kit contains enough templates to make up to 16 different polyhedra shapes. Hang them on the wall, above a mantle, inside or outside, garlands are a neat way to add a colourful design element to any room.

INCLUDED
* 5 different shapes
* 16 templates
* string
* instructions

B.Y.O.
* ruler & scissors / blade
* blunt pointy object
* glue or tape
* large needle

Designed and printed in Adelaide using 100% post consumer recycled paper. Mailed to you in a rigid cardboard mailer for protection.

name: Heidi & Baby Pip
description:
Our Dinky-Dye 'Cut & Sew' Kits are designed in Adelaide using eco-friendly materials. Each cute Aussie character is printed onto 100% super soft organic cotton sateen, and the fluffy toy fill provided is made in Australia from recycled plastic water bottles! INCLUDED * organic cotton template of Koala friends Heidi & Baby Pip * recycled non-allergenic fiber toy fill * detailed instructions B.Y.O. * scissors and iron * needle and thread * sewing machine (optional)

For a photographic tutorial please visit the Messagemark Blog for step by step instructions on how to make your Softie.

name: Polyhedra Gift Tags
description:
Gift Tags from Messagemark are small enough to hang on presents but large enough to write your special greeting. Handy for little notes and messages, you could try hanging them on wine bottles, door handles, presents, flowers, coffee cups, pens, bags, windscreen wipers - even your cat!

Brighten someone's day, make them feel all warm and fuzzy inside and let them know you are thinking of them. It will make you feel good too!

name: Nature CD Card
description:
If you are 'snap happy' with your digital camera then you are likely to be the kind of person who loves sharing your digital photos. Our unique CD card is designed for sharing your digital media - photos, video and music files.

And of course the CD card doubles as a greeting card so you can include your own personal message. Our CD Card looks more like a gift, so is the perfect package to share precious memories. 

The CD Card is supplied with an envelope and blank CD to share digital media. 
Size 150 x 150 mm

Some ideas on how you could use the CD card...
• Make a special present for a friend by creating a music compilation CD.
• Share photos after an event i.e. wedding, birthday, anniversary, christening, etc.
• Send files to a client with a personal message
• Create your own short movie and send copies out in a CD Card
• Burn your creative portfolio to disc and package in a CD Card
• Burn your product catalogue to CD for posting to customers
• Have the CD card personalised with your business logo

Gift Tags from Messagemark are small enough to hang on presents but large enough to write your special greeting. Handy for little notes and messages, you could try hanging them on wine bottles, door handles, presents, flowers, coffee cups, pens, bags, windscreen wipers - even your cat!

Brighten someone's day, make them feel all warm and fuzzy inside and let them know you are thinking of them. It will make you feel good too!

Pack Includes:
10 x Gift Tags (hole punched)
2 Tags in each design from the Organic Elements range
Tag Size 65 x 100 mm 

Designed and made in Adelaide by Kyrie Kohlhagen using 100% Recycled Paper.

name: Balloon Print
description:
Hanging on a wall or standing on a shelf, Messagemark cute and colorful prints will brighten any room at home or work.

Digitally printed onto heavy weight 350gsm recycled (post consumer waste) paper, each print is designed to make you and our earth feel happy!

The affordable range of Wall Art from Messagemark are designed to fit perfectly into the *RIBBA 30 x 40cm frame from IKEA.

Available in birch, walnut, black, white and silver, there are many options to suit your own interior color schemes. Simply place the print behind the mount board that comes with the *RIBBA frame and voila, instant art!

Each print comes packaged in a cello bag and is posted in a rigid cardboard envelope for protection.

Print Size: 320 x 400mm
Image Size 210 x 300mm

*RIBBA frame is not included with the print purchase.

name: Winter Wonderland Postcards
description:
A Postcard is something that hangs around for a while. We find people often keep them next to their desk, stuck on the fridge at home, or even frame as a mini artwork - it is a constant reminder of who sent it to them!

So experiment a little and see if our Postcards can help you to establish a better relationship with a Customer, or use them for a quick note to show your appreciation to someone special.

Pack Includes:
15 x Postcards*
3 Cards in each design from the Winter Wonderland range
Card Size 105 x 150 mm 

Designed and made in Adelaide by Kyrie Kohlhagen using 100% Recycled Paper.

*not supplied with envelopes

name: Retro Owl CD Card
description:
If you are 'snap happy' with your digital camera then you are likely to be the kind of person who loves sharing your digital photos. Our unique CD card is designed for sharing your digital media - photos, video and music files.

And of course the CD card doubles as a greeting card so you can include your own personal message. Our CD Card looks more like a gift, so is the perfect package to share precious memories. 

The CD Card is supplied with an envelope and blank CD to share digital media. 
Size 150 x 150 mm

Some ideas on how you could use the CD card...
• Make a special present for a friend by creating a music compilation CD.
• Share photos after an event i.e. wedding, birthday, anniversary, christening, etc.
• Send files to a client with a personal message
• Create your own short movie and send copies out in a CD Card
• Burn your creative portfolio to disc and package in a CD Card
• Burn your product catalogue to CD for posting to customers
• Have the CD card personalised with your business logo

name: Nigel the Kookaburra
description:
Our Dinky-Dye 'Cut & Sew' Kits are designed in Adelaide using eco-friendly materials. Each cute Aussie character is printed onto 100% super soft organic cotton sateen, and the fluffy toy fill provided is made in Australia from recycled plastic water bottles! INCLUDED * organic cotton template of our friend Nigel the Kookaburra * recycled non-allergenic fiber toy fill * detailed instructions B.Y.O. * scissors and iron * needle and thread * sewing machine (optional)

For a photographic tutorial please visit the Messagemark Blog for step by step instructions on how to make your Softie.
